---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { STATS } from '../data/siteStats';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about xConvert24.com — a free, fast, and ad-light unit conversion and calculator platform built for everyday use." keywords="about xConvert24, unit converter website, free online tools, conversion website, about us">
  <div class="max-w-3xl prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">About xConvert24.com</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      xConvert24.com is a free online conversion and calculator platform designed to give you instant, accurate results without clutter. No pop-ups, no mandatory sign-ups — just the tools you need, when you need them.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We believe everyday conversions should be effortless. Whether you're a student converting units for homework, a traveller checking currency rates, a cook scaling a recipe, or an engineer comparing pressure units — we want to be the one tool you bookmark and keep coming back to.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">What We Offer</h2>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>{STATS.total}+ converters and calculators</strong> — from weight, length, and temperature to scientific calculators, loan amortization, and colour pickers.</li>
      <li><strong>Instant results</strong> — all calculations happen in your browser. Nothing is sent to a server.</li>
      <li><strong>Dark mode</strong> — easy on the eyes, day or night.</li>
      <li><strong>Mobile-friendly</strong> — fully responsive on phones, tablets, and desktops.</li>
      <li><strong>No account required</strong> — use everything for free, forever.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Built With</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      xConvert24.com is built with <a href="https://astro.build" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>, styled with <a href="https://tailwindcss.com" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tailwind CSS</a>, and deployed globally on <a href="https://workers.cloudflare.com" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Workers</a> for fast load times worldwide.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Accuracy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We use industry-standard conversion factors sourced from NIST, ISO, and established scientific references. Currency rates are reference approximations — for live trading rates, always use a financial service. If you spot an error, please <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
